Class GetCacheRequest<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the type of object that is expected to be in the cache

    public class GetCacheRequest<V>
extends CacheRequest
    This class is the type of request for retrieving an object from the cache service. The parameter type on this class is used to specify the type of the cache retrieval.
